地时间 2024 年 12 月 31 日，乌克兰最大私营电力企业 DTEK 证实，乌克兰已收到从美国发出的第一批液化天然气（LNG），约有 1 亿立方米。 2024 年 12 月 27 日，乌克兰 DTEK 公司在希腊港口接收了这批货物。这批液化天然气被重新气化，然后输送至乌克兰。 此前，乌克兰 DTEK 公司于 2024 年 6 月与美国维吉液化天然气公司（Venture Global LNG）签署了供应协议，该协议是乌克兰与美国之间达成的首个重要液化天然气合同。根据该合同，乌克兰可以在 2026 年前从维吉液化天然气公司购买未指定数量的液化天然气。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-b46d6573830f02b6fb31ab4861985f62_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "41 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/8426728926"}}, "attached_info": "CkEI6oyytt+d5dpYEAMaCTExMjY2MTcwMyDqn9O7BjAAOIkHQBRyCjg0MjY3Mjg5MjZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1735812678.115534", "card_id": "Q_4847825358", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 546}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果有一个「一键冬眠」的按钮，你会按下去吗？为什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-5fafa053708cd974320fd327d31fd7fb_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "41 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/4847825358"}}, "attached_info": "CkEI6oyytt+d5dpYEAMaCTExMTk0NjIwNyCwqIG6BjAAOMAEQBVyCjQ4NDc4MjUzNTh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1735812678.115744", "card_id": "Q_3082627376", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 72}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "职场管理中，如何平衡「谁能干，谁干」与「该谁干，谁干」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-787a16db4c40d825720d4a4ad71b059c_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "40 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1